1. Imam veliku *volju* da putujem (I have a great desire to travel)
2. Ona je pokazala *volju* da uči strane jezike (She showed the will to learn foreign languages)
3. *Volja* je važan faktor za ostvarenje ciljeva (Will is an important factor in achieving goals)
4. On neće raditi ništa bez *volje* svoje majke (He won't do anything without his mother's consent)
5. *Volja* naroda je izražena na izborima (The will of the people is expressed in elections)
6. Dugo sam se borio sa *voljom* da prestanem pušiti (I struggled for a long time with the will to quit smoking)
7. Bez *volje* nema uspeha u životu (Without will, there is no success in life)
8. Nisam imao *volju* da učim za ispit (I didn't have the will to study for the exam)
9. Želim da pomognem, ali nemam *volje* za to danas (I want to help, but I don't have the will for it today)
10. Sve je stvar *volje*, ako hoćeš uspeti, uspećeš (It's all a matter of will, if you want to succeed, you will succeed)